  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Schritt 3 von 4: Fotos + Link an Voting-Gruppe senden\n\n**Was passiert hier:**\n1. Alle Kandidaten mit Status=`fotos_geladen` laden\n2. Pro Kandidat: sendMediaGroup (Foto-Album) oder sendMessage (kein Foto)\n3. NocoDB updaten: Status → `gesendet`, TelegramMsgId speichern\n4. Zusammenfassung in Admin-Gruppe senden\n\n**⚠️ Einmalig eintragen:**\n- `VOTING_GRUPPE_CHAT_ID` → Chat-ID der Telegram Voting-Gruppe-Liste\n- Umgebungsvariable `TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN` in n8n Settings setzen",
        "height": 200,
        "width": 540
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        0,
        0
      ],
      "id": "34a905c6-7981-4405-86f2-d3540c5eccb9",
      "name": "Info"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "lv-telegram-sender",
        "responseMode": "lastNode",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        0,
        384
      ],
      "id": "8f83b69d-2c40-4624-be6d-c72b54151829",
      "name": "🔗 Webhook Trigger",
      "webhookId": "lv-telegram-sender"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "url": "=https://nocodb.f3-events.de/api/v1/db/data/noco/pu4jkb0uwe4ebev/m9qmqh26mhpnlld?where=(Status,eq,fotos_geladen)&limit=50",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "xc-token",
              "value": "2l1BhPzXFj_Bb4pv9rKGpBMPZDkzpnKik7biab9-"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "timeout": 10000
        }
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [
        208,
        384
      ],
      "id": "ac3964f2-6acf-41ae-971f-a3964a7cb8ad",
      "name": "📋 Kandidaten fotos_geladen laden"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const records = $input.first().json.list || [];\n\nif (records.length === 0) {\n  console.log('Keine Kandidaten mit Status=fotos_geladen.');\n  return [];\n}\n\nconst chatId = '-1003592524930';\nconst nl = String.fromCharCode(10);\n\nreturn records.map(r => {\n  const photos = (() => { try { return JSON.parse(r.Fotos || '[]'); } catch(e) { return []; } })();\n  const caption = '<b>' + (r.Username || 'Unbekannt') + '</b>'\n    + (r.EventName ? nl + '📅 ' + r.EventName : '')\n    + nl + '🔗 ' + r.ProfilUrl;\n\n  return { json: {\n    _nocodb_id: r.Id,\n    _chatId: chatId,\n    _caption: caption,\n    _photo: photos[0] || null\n  }};\n});"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        400,
        384
      ],
      "id": "45725689-bd1a-4bb9-b0bd-0670fe8dd41d",
      "name": "📦 Telegram Payload bauen"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": {
            "caseSensitive": true,
            "leftValue": "",
            "typeValidation": "strict"
          },
          "conditions": [
            {
              "id": "has-photo",
              "leftValue": "={{ $json._photo }}",
              "rightValue": "",
              "operator": {
                "type": "string",
                "operation": "notEmpty"
              }
            }
          ],
          "combinator": "and"
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        608,
        384
      ],
      "id": "lv3-if-photo",
      "name": "📷 Hat Foto?"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "https://api.telegram.org/bot8703335778:AAFxLDwYoTs1NXCPwfJvjO2bcEkZlrIDHG4/sendPhoto",
        "sendBody": true,
        "contentType": "raw",
        "rawContentType": "application/json",
        "body": "={{ JSON.stringify({ chat_id: $json._chatId, photo: $json._photo, caption: $json._caption, parse_mode: \"HTML\" }) }}",
        "options": {
          "timeout": 15000
        }
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [
        752,
        64
      ],
      "id": "lv3-send-photo",
      "name": "📸 Foto senden"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "https://api.telegram.org/bot8703335778:AAFxLDwYoTs1NXCPwfJvjO2bcEkZlrIDHG4/sendMessage",
        "sendBody": true,
        "contentType": "raw",
        "rawContentType": "application/json",
        "body": "={{ JSON.stringify({ chat_id: $json._chatId, text: $json._caption, parse_mode: \"HTML\" }) }}",
        "options": {
          "timeout": 15000
        }
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [
        1088,
        80
      ],
      "id": "lv3-send-msg",
      "name": "✏️ Text senden"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const result = $input.item.json.result || $input.item.json || {};\nconst nocodb_id = $('📦 Telegram Payload bauen').item.json._nocodb_id;\nconst isArray = Array.isArray(result);\nconst msgId = isArray ? (result[0]?.message_id || '') : (result.message_id || '');\nreturn [{ json: { _nocodb_id: nocodb_id, msgId: String(msgId) } }];"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        800,
        384
      ],
      "id": "352e038d-57de-4e73-84f3-2db46a3fcc2d",
      "name": "🔢 Message-ID extrahieren"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "PATCH",
        "url": "=https://nocodb.f3-events.de/api/v1/db/data/noco/pu4jkb0uwe4ebev/m9qmqh26mhpnlld/{{ $json._nocodb_id }}",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "xc-token",
              "value": "2l1BhPzXFj_Bb4pv9rKGpBMPZDkzpnKik7biab9-"
            },
            {
              "name": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ]
        },
        "sendBody": true,
        "contentType": "raw",
        "rawContentType": "application/json",
        "body": "={{ JSON.stringify({ Status: 'gesendet', TelegramMsgId: $json.msgId }) }}",
        "options": {
          "timeout": 10000
        }
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [
        1008,
        384
      ],
      "id": "a7630d06-b21b-42c6-9e35-3d9efc0a1ec9",
      "name": "💾 NocoDB updaten (gesendet)"
    },
